stages.playscript:
echo "push docker image"
        withCredentials([usernamePassword(credentialsId: 'rddhub.changhong.com', passwordVariable: 'dockerPassword', usernameVariable: 'dockerUser')]) {
            sh "docker login -u ${dockerUser} -p ${dockerPassword} rddhub.changhong.com"
            sh "docker push rddhub.changhong.com/sei/${params.PROJECT_NAME}:dev"
        }
        echo "remove docker image"
        sh "docker rmi rddhub.changhong.com/sei/${params.PROJECT_NAME}:dev"
